# Category Service Schema
# Manages product categories, subcategories, and category-specific specifications

## Tables:
# - categories (category_id, name, slug, icon, parent_id, level, sort_order, product_count, status, created_at)
# - category_specs (spec_id, category_id, spec_template, required_fields, optional_fields)

## Features:
# - Hierarchical categories (parent/child)
# - Category icons
# - Product count per category
# - Category-specific specification templates (30+ templates defined in types)
# - Electronics, Fashion, Home, Beauty, Sports, Books, etc.
# - Size charts per category (clothing, footwear, rings, mattress, etc.)
